WEBVTT

00:00:00.543 --> 00:00:03.286
10. marta 2011. godine,

00:00:03.286 --> 00:00:05.362
bio sam u MIT
laboratoriji u Kembridžu

00:00:05.362 --> 00:00:08.081
na sastanku sa fakultetom,

00:00:08.081 --> 00:00:10.020
studentima i osobljem,

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:11.551
pokušavali smo da se dogovorimo

00:00:11.551 --> 00:00:13.671
da li bih ja trebao
biti sledeći direktor.

00:00:13.671 --> 00:00:16.040
Te noći, u ponoć,

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:17.990
zemljotres jačine 9 stepeni po Rihteru

00:00:17.990 --> 00:00:20.676
pogodio je obalu Japana.

00:00:20.676 --> 00:00:22.961
Moja žena i porodica
su bili u Japanu,

00:00:22.961 --> 00:00:26.271
i kako su novosti pristizale,

00:00:26.271 --> 00:00:27.970
ja sam paničio.

00:00:27.970 --> 00:00:29.232
Gledao sam novosti

00:00:29.232 --> 00:00:32.060
i slušao konferencije za štampu